description: This timer remote cord with DC adapter for your Canon RS-60E3 will allow you to easily capture photos with different timed exposures. Timer settings from 1 second to 59 minutes to 99 hours. Easy dial for entering numeric settings. Backlit LCD display. Remote shutter release. Features: Self-timer; Interval timer; Long-exposure timer; Exposure-count setting. Cord length: 4 ft. Includes: Remote unit / cord; 2.5 mm DC adapter. Compatible With Canon: EOS 60D / EOS 600D / EOS Kiss X5 / EOS 1100D / EOS Kiss X50 / EOS 550D / EOS Kiss Digital X4 / EOS 500D / EOS 1000D / EOS 450D/ Digital Rebel / Digital Rebel T1i / Digital Rebel T2i / Digital Rebel T3 / Digital Rebel T3i / Digital Rebel X / Digital Rebel XS / Digital Rebel XSi / Digital Rebel XT / Digital Rebel XTi / ELAN 7 / ELAN 7E / ELAN 7N / ELAN II / ELAN IIE / IX LITE / Rebel 2000 / Rebel G / Rebel G II.
title: eForCity Timer Remote Cord with 2.5 mm DC Adapter Compatible with Canon RS-60E3, 4FT
